<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我昨天<delay8 />因為收到聖誕老人的
禮物太過高興，<delay20 />結果晚上就
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夢到聖誕老人了喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這都是多虧你<delay20 />
將禮物送來給我！<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />謝謝你啦！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧昨天<delay20 />收到了
聖誕老人送的禮物，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天也是幹勁滿滿啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年也要保持這個狀態<delay20 />
繼續收禮物喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
謝謝你的聖誕禮物！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我超開心的！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧這樣，<delay8 />我昨晚有夢到<delay20 />
變成聖誕老人的你喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你昨天的<delay20 />聖誕禮物啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我因為太過開心，<delay20 />醒來才發現
自己抱著禮物睡著了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年也請你多多關照啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />昨天能收到<tag a="110" b="3" />和<delay8 />
聖誕老人送的禮物，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是最棒的一天了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是聖誕老人的禮物就足夠讓人開心了，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再加上<delay8 />來自好對手的禮物，<delay20 />
開心程度就變成兩倍囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你昨天的禮物！<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很高興能收到來自
你和聖誕老人的<delay20 />兩份禮物喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你果然是我最棒的<delay20 />
好對手兼摯友！<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很期待明年的禮物喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今天是聖誕節，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你接下來<delay8 />有什麼預定嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我自己是<delay8 />不管聖誕節還是平日，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />行程表上都滿是健身的預定喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">昨天不是平安夜嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我本來<delay8 />打算見聖誕老人一面，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以晚上很努力地保持清醒……<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等回過神來才發現自己睡著了，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果今年也沒能見到他，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>